Margot Bryant https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Margot_Bryant 0 Kathleen Mary Margaret Bryant (8 March 1897 – 1 January 1988), professionally known as Margot Bryant was an English actress, of stage, television and film best known for playing Minnie Caldwell on the soap opera Coronation Street from its inception in 1960 until 1976 (episode 1589).
